_sText: Ok... right this is the 3rd and final time i am editing this map exept for when i do another version of it... it is a small but sweet map with lots of exciting secrets. i have basically just edited the ramps to make them smoother and either put in some more secrets or made them better. i hope you enjoy playing on my map and it does get alot better when u firgure out where and what each 5 secrets do :P
